entries.album: The Dark Side of The Moon

entries.review: Beautiful, beautiful, beautiful. Makes me want to get way better at the guitar.  I think I will listen to this album forever and show my children someday. Favorite song: Place to Be.
This album feels like going back to my hometown and finding beauty in a place that is otherwise decrepit and awful. Or not really beauty, but accepting it for what it is. Favorite song is Quarry.
Warhol banana album. I listened to this while eating grocery sushi with the California sun on my back, which was quite beautiful. Incredible listen. Favorite song is There She Goes Again.
